45
00:02:59,530 --> 00:03:00,860
Then why cover your face?

46
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:06,360
Tell me the truth.

47
00:03:11,130 --> 00:03:12,730
I drank too much

48
00:03:15,060 --> 00:03:16,500
last night.

49
00:03:16,730 --> 00:03:17,570
Then,

50
