104
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,400
Lu Group.

105
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:18,100
Don't you know the old man always
wanted to work with them?

106
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:19,300
What now?

107
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,360
Got a problem with that?

108
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,900
Legal Boy.

109
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,440
Just you wait.

110
00:05:28,060 --> 00:05:28,900
Dad,

111
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,300
