127
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:10,500
I'm here to help you.

128
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,400
Legal Boy.

129
00:06:13,130 --> 00:06:14,060
If I

130
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:15,130
help you,

131
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,800
