132
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:20,800
Miss Lu,

133
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:22,800
shall we

134
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,130
make a deal?

135
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:26,930
A deal?

136
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,360
Tell me more.

137
00:06:30,265 --> 00:06:31,736
If you can help me find the culprit,

138
00:06:33,100 --> 00:06:35,060
