143
00:06:47,530 --> 00:06:48,700
I'm not part of the Zhangs.

144
00:06:50,330 --> 00:06:51,330
Once I find the culprit,

145
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:53,130
and it's resolved,

146
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:54,930
I'll have nothing

147
00:06:54,930 --> 00:06:56,130
